<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Yellow Wiggle Emma Watkins has just bought a new puppy with her musician boyfriend, Oliver Brian. </p>

<p>The 30-year-old was spotted holding the adorable pet pooch on Tuesday, as she and Oliver loaded belongings into their car in Sydney, where they are based. </p>

<p>It comes after Emma sweetly congratulated her ex-husband, Purple Wiggle Lachy Gillespie, on the birth of his twins with his ballet dancer fiancée, Dana Stephensen.</p>

<p>What a fluff ball! Yellow Wiggle Emma Watkins and boyfriend Oliver Brian have gotten an adorable new puppy and were seen with the pet pooch in Sydney on Tuesday</p>

<p>On Tuesday, the redhead doted on her tiny puppy and carried it close to her chest. </p>

<p>She was dressed casually in a maroon dress and stockings and wore a thick headband in her hair.</p>

<p>Emma could also be seen loading up her car with puppy pads, no doubt to help toilet train the fluffy pup. </p>

