<p>New man: Pictured is Emma's new boyfriend Oliver Brian</p>

<p>At one point, Oliver, who is a musician with The Wiggles, carried their new puppy as they gathered their belongings.</p>

<p>The 32-year-old also cut a casual figure in a blue shirt and black trousers. </p>

